description:
Includes 2 sizes - alt .css for smaller size is available

Installed to /var/mobile/Library/LockHTML (for LS) and /SBHTML (for HS)

Apply with Xen HTML 1.x or 2.0

Requires XenInfo for weather/battery components to work properly on Xen HTML 1.x
